IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. INVENTORY.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 STOCK       PIC 999.
01 ORDER-QTY   PIC 999.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MAIN.
    DISPLAY "CURRENT STOCK:"
    ACCEPT STOCK

    DISPLAY "ORDER QUANTITY:"
    ACCEPT ORDER-QTY

    IF ORDER-QTY <= STOCK
        SUBTRACT ORDER-QTY FROM STOCK
        DISPLAY "ORDER APPROVED"
        DISPLAY "REMAINING: " STOCK
    ELSE
        DISPLAY "INSUFFICIENT STOCK"
    END-IF

    STOP RUN.